languages.text: "Подозреваемый Ярт сообщил, что оболгать себя его подбила Джиневри. Что скажешь в свое оправдание?"
"Suspect Yart claims that you coerced him into lying about himself, Jinevri. What do you have to say for yourself?"
languages.original_text: "Подозреваемый Ярт сообщил, что оболгать себя его подбила Джиневри. Что скажешь в свое оправдание?"

traits.locale_text: "Suspect Yart claimed that he had been encouraged to lie about himself by Jinevra. What do you have to say for yourself?"
"Hrotko, you painted fake symbols of corruption on the worker and coerced him into giving a false confession. I am waiting for an explanation."

languages.text: « Le suspect Yart prétend que vous lui avez extorqué de faux aveux, Jinevri. Qu'avez-vous à dire pour votre défense ? »
languages.original_text: "Suspect Yart claims that you coerced him into lying about himself, Jinevri. What do you have to say for yourself?"

traits.locale_text: « Le suspect Yart prétend que vous lui avez extorqué de faux aveux, Jinevri. Qu'avez-vous à dire pour votre défense ? »
« Hrotko, vous avez tracé de faux symboles de corruption sur cet ouvrier et vous lui avez extorqué de faux aveux. J'exige des explications. »

languages.text: «El sospechoso Yart afirma que lo coaccionó para que mintiera sobre sí mismo, Jinevri. ¿Qué tiene que decir al respecto?».
languages.original_text: "Suspect Yart claims that you coerced him into lying about himself, Jinevri. What do you have to say for yourself?"

traits.locale_text: «El sospechoso Yart afirma que lo coaccionó para que mintiera sobre sí mismo, Jinevri. ¿Qué tiene que decir al respecto?».
«Hrotko, pintaste símbolos falsos de corrupción en el trabajador y le obligaste a realizar una confesión falsa. Espero una explicación».

languages.text: “那个叫亚特的嫌疑人声称你逼他说谎。你对此有什么要解释的吗，杰尼娃？”
languages.original_text: "Suspect Yart claims that you coerced him into lying about himself, Jinevri. What do you have to say for yourself?"

traits.locale_text: “那个叫亚特的嫌疑人声称你逼他说谎。你对此有什么要解释的吗，杰尼娃？”
“赫洛卡，你在那个工人身上画了拙劣的腐化符号，还强迫他做出了虚假的供词，这件事情你得解释解释。”

languages.text: 「ヤート容疑者は、お前が嘘をつくよう強要したと主張している、ジネヴリ。何か言い分はあるか？」
languages.original_text: "Suspect Yart claims that you coerced him into lying about himself, Jinevri. What do you have to say for yourself?"

traits.locale_text: 「ヤート容疑者は、お前が嘘をつくよう強要したと主張している、ジネヴリ。何か言い分はあるか？」
「フロトコ、あなたは労働者に偽の汚職のシンボルを描き、虚偽の自白を強要した。これについて、説明するんだ」

languages.text: "Der Verdächtige Yart behauptet, Ihr hättet ihn gezwungen, zu lügen, Jinevri. Was habt Ihr dazu zu sagen?"
languages.original_text: "Suspect Yart claims that you coerced him into lying about himself, Jinevri. What do you have to say for yourself?"

traits.locale_text: "Der Verdächtige Yart behauptet, Ihr hättet ihn gezwungen, zu lügen, Jinevri. Was habt Ihr dazu zu sagen?"
"Hrotko, Ihr habt falsche Symbole der Verderbnis auf den Arbeiter gemalt und ihn zu einem falschen Geständnis gezwungen. Ich erwarte eine Erklärung."

languages.text: "Şüpheli Yart, zorla ona yalan söylettiğini iddia ediyor Jinevri. Kendini savunmak için ne söyleyeceksin?"
languages.original_text: "Suspect Yart claims that you coerced him into lying about himself, Jinevri. What do you have to say for yourself?"
